# Test Scenarios – The Skill App (Mobile)

## TS01 – App Installation
Verify app installs successfully from the app store.

## TS02 – App Launch
Verify app launches without crashing.

## TS03 – User Registration
Verify user can register with valid details.

## TS04 – Login Functionality
Verify registered user can log in successfully.

## TS05 – Appointment Creation
Verify user can create a new appointment.

## TS06 – Appointment Editing
Verify existing appointment can be edited.

## TS07 – Appointment Deletion
Verify user can delete an appointment.

## TS08 – Call Management
Verify user can log, view, or manage calls.

## TS09 – Notifications & Reminders
Verify reminders are triggered for scheduled appointments.

## TS10 – Navigation
Verify navigation between screens works smoothly.

## TS11 – Form Validation
Verify validation messages for mandatory fields.

## TS12 – Error Handling
Verify proper error messages for invalid actions.
